Distribution. Confined to a coastal strip near Karratha and Roebourne in the Pilbara region, Western Australia (
Fig. 1
). The westernmost record is from Mardie Pool, with the easternmost record 200 km distant at Balla Balla Creek (~ 50 km east of Roebourne). Records occur from the coast and inland to about 40 km . Thus the total range of this species at current estimate is approximately 5,000 km 2 .
